  "investment": {
    "headings": [],
    "paragraphs": [
      "I am glad to see you on my page. One of the closest investments is an investment in yourself. I invite you to check my price list.",
      "Birth Package:",
      "I’m happy to support both hospital and home births.",
      "£1700, in total, and requires a deposit of £1000. This includes my transport expenses.",
      "As I l work toward certification with Doula UK, I’ll be working as a Mentored Doula for four births, with the guidance of an experienced doula.",
      "For the first four births, I will offer my services at a very reduced fee: £1000! The only catch? A short review form after my last visit.",
      "It is important to me that my services are accessible, so I am happy to be flexible with instalments and the duration of your payment plan. Please reach out if you would like to discuss this further.",
      "Postnatal Packages:",
      "Gentle Start – £300",
      "Nurtured Nest – £580",
      "Sacred Fourth Trimester – £1,100",
      "Ceremonies:",
      "Closing the bones: £180",
      "Mother blessing: £150",
      "Placenta Burial Ceremony: £120",
      "First menarche Celebration: £150"
    ],
